      "fix": "Add --headless flag to the export command: 'xvfb-run \"$GODOT_BIN\" --headless --path ... --export-release'. The --headless flag tells Godot to skip display server initialization entirely, bypassing Vulkan. May also be able to drop xvfb-run from just the export step and use plain '--headless' without it.",
